{"tid":148180,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今天，拜仁慕尼黑殺死了足球","createTime":"2017-03-08T11:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T14:19:57.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f94e068ff076806baddff4de660a3762c48617c8","tid":148180,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"個人來說，我一直以來最憎的就是德甲波。<br />\n<br />\n他是唯一令我聯想到機械人踢波的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n從他們最擅長射十二碼就可窺探一二。只有像訓練軍人一樣，抹殺人類情緒，才可確保十二碼穩定的表現。<br />\n<br />\n在球場上，射十二碼，叫劊子手。<br />\n<br />\n至於甚麼走位最機動，戰術最規律等等，說穿了就是把個人的想像、發揮，壓到最低。再把所謂團隊精神無限推高，高層在背後作充滿計算的數據分析，然後下達嚴格指令，球員聽命執行。<br />\n<br />\n所以他們出色的球員，只有指揮型精神領袖，沒有藝術家一般的球星。D哥斯達算是一個異類，不過今天你都唔太見到佢。<br />\n<br />\n而現今足球愈來愈不可觀，就是因為這種意識已成主導。<br />\n<br />\n當足球愈發容不下個人的自發演繹，當利雲杜夫斯基的「穩定」正式超越朗拿度的「隨機」，足球已死。<br />\n<br />\n除下頭盔，準備中箭，讓我說句，識得欣賞足球，你係唔會亦唔應該捧拜仁既。"},{"pid":"d83cb096aaa87a1b08cdfe23a5f242f15159074c","tid":148180,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:16:33.000Z","msg":"愛心暖帖黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b3a7dd7cf33b6c6dd4353fd469b5d47160d303","tid":148180,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"有me既拜仁等於藝術"},{"pid":"186a6871cf555935c9f6cead2792218923475024","tid":148180,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺的華麗足球贏十條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a832461b4919fbc218d986aace0fe24ff6cf03","tid":148180,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"本身係咪德國炒鳩巴西之後寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbf1a874ac95b1454163a873afc8e1932319839","tid":148180,"uid":58622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺足球充滿人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24979a2c53bedd2c068c834aa4f8ebbd19c61fc1","tid":148180,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身係咪德國炒鳩巴西之後寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddd01807b6465e16ead6f6ffc11c718abce57b9","tid":148180,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身係咪德國炒鳩巴西之後寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a931f664e7496a25169de4bf3c32d5ba539a2eb","tid":148180,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身係咪德國炒鳩巴西之後寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再早d"},{"pid":"1528641a502aa88b85372c7e873ad9a5299c82ee","tid":148180,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89f10980edf0b434bf4f257d7e1d699e1afce0e5","tid":148180,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T01:27:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"691e57d8bfe90c368484cf2cdd4d9154ff2cb698","tid":148180,"uid":21851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"三分已袋"},{"pid":"07a5817556fdfd1